Optional Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
DataobjectManager


Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------

Extend your Custom Page from Cu3erPage ie;
class CustomPage extends Cu3erPage {

Extend your CustomPage Controller as normal ie;
class CustomPage_Controller extends Page_Controller {

Include the function;
public function FlashCu3er(){
 return new Cu3erPage_Holder($this->ID);
}

Put $FlashCu3er in your template


